description: Returns a list of existing cache reports for all file shares associated with your Amazon Web Services account. This list includes all information provided by the DescribeCacheReport action, such as report name, status, completion progress, start time, end time, filters, and tags.

nested_items.name: CacheReportList
nested_items.description: A list of existing cache reports for all file shares associated with your Amazon Web Services account. This list includes all information provided by the DescribeCacheReport action, such as report status, completion progress, start time, end time, filters, and tags.

nested_items.name: CacheReportARN
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the cache report you want to describe.

nested_items.name: CacheReportStatus
nested_items.description: The status of the specified cache report.

nested_items.name: ReportCompletionPercent
nested_items.description: The percentage of the report generation process that has been completed at time of inquiry.

nested_items.name: EndTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the gateway stopped generating the cache report.

nested_items.name: Role
nested_items.description: The ARN of the IAM role that an S3 File Gateway assumes when it accesses the underlying storage.

nested_items.name: FileShareARN
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the file share.

nested_items.name: LocationARN
nested_items.description: The ARN of the Amazon S3 bucket location where the cache report is saved.

nested_items.name: StartTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the gateway started generating the cache report.

nested_items.name: InclusionFilters
nested_items.description: The list of filters and parameters that determine which files are included in the report.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The parameter name for a filter that determines which files are included or excluded from a cache report.

nested_items.name: Values
nested_items.description: The parameter value for a filter that determines which files are included or excluded from a cache report.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: ExclusionFilters
nested_items.description: The list of filters and parameters that determine which files are excluded from the report.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The parameter name for a filter that determines which files are included or excluded from a cache report.

nested_items.name: Values
nested_items.description: The parameter value for a filter that determines which files are included or excluded from a cache report.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: ReportName
nested_items.description: The file name of the completed cache report object stored in Amazon S3.

nested_items.name: Tags
nested_items.description: The list of key/value tags associated with the report.

nested_items.name: Key
nested_items.description: Tag key. The key can't start with aws:.

nested_items.name: Value
nested_items.description: Value of the tag key.

nested_items.name: Marker
nested_items.description: If the request includes Marker, the response returns that value in this field.
